      <br>
      <strong>Solution</strong>
      <br>
      <strong>Note:  + x - = - (i.e. product of Negative sign (-) and Positive sign (+) gives Negative result)</strong>
      <br>
      (+3) + (-7) = 3 – 7 = <strong>-4</strong>
      <br>
      <strong>The above means you have 3 (i.e. +3) and owe 7 (i.e. -7), if you give out the 3, you will need 4 (i.e. -4) to balance up.</strong>
      </div>
